<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Students with a score of 4 or 5 on Advanced Placement examinations in academic subjects may be eligible for college credit in pertinent courses; elective studio credit is granted for scores of 4 or 5 on AP examinations for General Studio or Drawing.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://inside.massart.edu/Academic_Resources/Advising_and_Registration/Academic_Advising/Transfer_Credit/Advanced_Placement_Program.html" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

